targets.query: SELECT last("project"), last("color"), last("rate"), last("notes") FROM "project" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1d), "employee" fill(null)
SELECT last("project"), last("color"), last("index"), last("notes") FROM "uaproject" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1d), "index" fill(null)

SELECT (count("rate")-count("workingDay")) as "Tage", 100*(count("rate")-count("workingDay"))/count("workingDay") as "Auslastung", (sum("rate")/(count("rate")-count("workingDay"))) as "Durch. Tagessatz", sum("rate") as "Umsatz" FROM "project" WHERE employee='$employee' AND $timeFilter AND ("rate" > 0 OR "workingDay"=true) GROUP BY "YM"

Tagessatz", sum("rate") as "Umsatz" FROM "project" WHERE employee='$employee' AND $timeFilter AND (("rate"  > 0  AND (status='hard booked' OR status='soft booked')) OR "workingDay"=true) GROUP BY "YM"
